dcterms:description: A database containing 26,650 live frames from 685 subjects and 32,910 spoof frames made from 7 materials with 14 variants, used for training and evaluating fingerprint spoof detection methods.

dcterms:description: A dataset used for Government Controlled Test (GCT-3) at Johns Hopkins University Applied Physics Laboratory, which includes diverse biometric data for evaluating spoof detection systems.
dcterms:title: Government Controlled Test (GCT-3) at Johns Hopkins University Applied Physics Laboratory (JHUAPL)
